  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      UIC Division of pediatric surgery has IRB approval to perform retrospective and prospective&#xD;
      study of their pediatric surgical patients. At UIC Dr. Lobe performed the first known single&#xD;
      port robotic splenectomy on a child and as a surgical first this case is worthy of a case&#xD;
      report. Since it is a surgical and therapeutic first it needs to be aon regestiry of health&#xD;
      research prior to publication.&#xD;
